Part of me is wondering how much pressure this puts on WotC to make sure there are no leaks for the set. I'm sure their plan to reveal everything to tell the whole story is probably more grand and elaborate than anything they've done, a leak would certainly ruin a TON of work they've put in, more so than normal sets
It would have to be worse than the New Phyrexia leak, right? Like, that was big and important, but anything in WAR getting spoiled would really suck.
They've been building up the story for this set for dang near 9 months now, it would be a massive suck

To be a pedant, I don’t think anything could be as bad as the NPH leak.

To be more on-topic, i think the severity of a leak would depend on WHAT gets leaked.
Promos being leaked wouldn’t be a big deal because it always happened. They’d plan around it. Unless we had multiple story spotlights leaked I don’t think it would be an issue.

Outside of an obvious “Climax” card.
Right, but with everything going on in this set and all the build up, even one key "climax" card getting spoiled could ruin soooooo much that would lead up to it
I’m also probably focusing on the wrong aspect of this. I absolutely agree that anything of importance being leaked would be a major blow to creative.
